                    <span id="c-1042072889" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1042072889" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1042072889">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/carmelita/">Xaos Geneto</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">重点读了意识形态国家机器，马基雅维利，列宁这几篇，有关科学的文章非常重要，以后还要再读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
